  "page": "Clegane (founder)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\"><img alt=\"House Clegane.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/50px-House_Clegane.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/75px-House_Clegane.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/100px-House_Clegane.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Clegane</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\"><img alt=\"House Clegane.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/50px-House_Clegane.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/75px-House_Clegane.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b6/House_Clegane.svg/100px-House_Clegane.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Clegane_Founder_(Histories_and_Lore).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Clegane Founder (Histories and Lore).png\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png/350px-Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png\" width=\"350\" height=\"315\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/79/Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png/525px-Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/79/Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png/700px-Clegane_Founder_%28Histories_and_Lore%29.png 2x\" /></a><div>The founder of House Clegane, when he was a kennelmaster, with his dogs. From <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>: Histories and Lore © HBO</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kennelmaster\" title=\"Kennelmaster\">Kennelmaster</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Ser</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane%27s_Keep\" title=\"Clegane&#39;s Keep\">Clegane's Keep</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">House Clegane</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\nUnknown</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Issue</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Clegane_(father_of_Gregor_and_Sandor)\" title=\"Clegane (father of Gregor and Sandor)\">son</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Clegane</b> was the founder of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">House Clegane</a> and the first <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">Knight</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane%27s_Keep\" title=\"Clegane&#39;s Keep\">Clegane's Keep</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> His first name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clegane_(founder)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unknowclegane.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Unknowclegane.jpg/350px-Unknowclegane.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"306\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/08/Unknowclegane.jpg/525px-Unknowclegane.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/08/Unknowclegane.jpg/700px-Unknowclegane.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Unknowclegane.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The kennelmaster saves <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">Tytos Lannister</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Lioness\" title=\"Lioness\">lioness</a>. © tumcolho</div></div></div>\n<p>Clegane was originally the <a href=\"/index.php/Kennelmaster\" title=\"Kennelmaster\">kennelmaster</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. One <a href=\"/index.php/Autumn\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Autumn\">autumn</a> year, Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">Tytos Lannister</a> came between a <a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">lioness</a> and her prey. The lioness killed Tytos's horse and was about to attack him as well, when the kennelmaster came to his rescue with his <a href=\"/index.php/Hound\" title=\"Hound\">hounds</a>, losing his leg and three dogs in the effort. As a reward, Tytos granted the kennelmaster a <a href=\"/index.php/Knighthood\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Knighthood\">knighthood</a>, lands and a <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane%27s_Keep\" title=\"Clegane&#39;s Keep\">towerhouse</a>, and took <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane_(father_of_Gregor_and_Sandor)\" title=\"Clegane (father of Gregor and Sandor)\">his son</a> as his <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>, thereby creating <a href=\"/index.php/House_Clegane\" title=\"House Clegane\">House Clegane</a>. For his <a href=\"/index.php/Sigil\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sigil\">sigil</a>, Ser Clegane chose the three dogs he lost saving Tytos, on a yellow field like autumn grass.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clegane_(founder)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>A drunken <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a> tells the origins of his house to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clegane_(founder)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><a href=\"/index.php/Lion\" title=\"Lion\">Bitch</a> tore into <a href=\"/index.php/Tytos_Lannister\" title=\"Tytos Lannister\">my lord</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horse</a> and would have done for my lord too, but my grandfather came up with the <a href=\"/index.php/Dog\" title=\"Dog\">hounds</a>. Three of his dogs died running her off. My grandfather lost a leg, so Lannister paid him for it with lands and a <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane%27s_Keep\" title=\"Clegane&#39;s Keep\">towerhouse</a>, and took <a href=\"/index.php/Clegane_(father_of_Gregor_and_Sandor)\" title=\"Clegane (father of Gregor and Sandor)\">his son</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a>. The three dogs on our banner are the three that died, in the yellow of autumn grass. A hound will die for you, but never lie to you.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok18.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Clegane_(founder)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Clegane</a></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\">Unknown<br />wife</td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowsp